"{\"uid\": \"localnews8.com-news-2024-07-27-ukraine-shows-off-culture-to-olympics-fans-and-looks-for-wartime-support-with-clubhouse\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Associated Press  PARIS (AP) - Ukraine opened a hospitality house Saturday at the 2024 Olympics in Paris - its first during any Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999231848758292, \"rank\": 7.624112299608378e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9881483695927638, \"rank\": 0.0113741231989902, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999986797299318, \"rank\": 1.3202717156383415e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will bring concerts from the country's most beloved artists and a tasting of traditional cuisine in a bid to promote local culture and raise awareness about the war with Russia.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9987775163817179, \"rank\": 0.0004712539262359139, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 100 members of the public were invited to the official opening, shouting \\\"Viva la France\\\" and \\\"Glory to Ukraine\\\" in a show of suppor